    "16370500283483070c": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1637050028a86ed12f-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "dog beds"
          }
        },
        "1637050028a86ed12f-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our dog beds are our absolute bestsellers. Unlike other dog beds they are filled with coconut fiber from Indonesia, which makes the dog bed very eco-friendly. <br/>The coconut tree is one of the fastest growing trees and the fiber can easily be composted once you don’t need the bed anymore. <br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "1637050028a86ed12f-2": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop Now",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/dog-beds"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1637050028a86ed12f-0",
        "1637050028a86ed12f-1",
        "1637050028a86ed12f-2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/kali-dogwear-0128_3x_c57ae5c9-f8c2-4e20-af33-0d51e_2_750x_7808ee3d-8f1b-4cdc-b881-5c335f7d5c31.jpg",
        "height": "adapt",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "layout": "image_first"
      }
    },
    "163783239760490887": {
      "type": "testimonial",
      "blocks": {
        "16378323974c21f457-0": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/70F0C985-952E-441C-8109-166897BCBF1C.png",
            "title1": "Locally produced in Indonesia",
            "text1": "<p>We work with producers that we treat like family. It takes a long time to find the perfect fit to work on a brand with high values. Most of our suppliers and partners are female business owners and we love it.</p>"
          }
        },
        "c1fba0e3-62a0-4b6d-a8e9-2eb4a0863979": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/C9C52DBC-EFAD-4A4E-A267-875AE4A2B5AC.png",
            "title1": "Handpicked materials",
            "text1": "<p>With an eye on sustainability, we choose our materials. We can’t be 100% sustainable. That is just impossible, but every day we try our best to be as eco-friendly as we can be.</p>"
          }
        },
        "65cc895e-f79c-4973-9b26-0441035f1557": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7BAA66D3-547B-44F3-95A6-F10441447294_86af789f-31c4-4e7c-b961-2fb471d03ba6.png",
            "title1": "No plastic",
            "text1": "<p>We have a no plastic policy. We always remind our producers to not use single use plastic wrap and we carefully pick our packaging.</p>"
          }
        },
        "8d63a031-7260-42ef-a653-1943f809bb14": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/88D12C88-99D1-4124-B3B6-84CE5605B354.png",
            "title1": "Impact",
            "text1": "<p>We give back 5% of our profit to help street dogs in need. <br/>We educate and raise awareness around animal welfare and pollution.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "16378323974c21f457-0",
