    "163780752758bd3144": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1637807527de32d37e-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "5% of sales support street dogs"
          }
        },
        "1637807527de32d37e-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Anyone who has visited Bali is well aware of the many street dogs on the island and has also likely witnessed their very sad and dangerous fate. We have never seen more suffering and cruelty against animals than here in Indonesia, and as long as there are no enforced laws, the dogs will continue to suffer. This reality is the reason why we started Kali Dogwear, to educate, raise awareness & make a positive impact on the lives of the local street dogs.<br/>We donate 5% of our profits to our charity partner, local dog rescue foundation, Bali Paws.</p>"
          }
        },
        "1637807527de32d37e-2": {
          "type": "button",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Read More",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1637807527de32d37e-0",
        "1637807527de32d37e-1",
        "1637807527de32d37e-2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2_750x_a7b95856-2fcc-4ac5-a19a-32cf7ac0927b.png",
        "height": "adapt",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "layout": "image_first"
      }
    },
    "1637807530a594268b": {
      "type": "testimonial",
      "blocks": {
        "1637807530288d7dd5-0": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Background_2_8dd2cebb-b1c5-4dff-b1d8-f6be4f58706c.png",
            "title1": "First Aid",
            "text1": "<p>Very severe cases have to go straight to the vet clinic to get treated. <br/>Broken bones, burns, distemper, Parvovirus – only to name a few can be life threatning.</p>"
          }
        },
        "d2c2cf8d-28d4-47cb-943c-5c089039a730": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/C9C52DBC-EFAD-4A4E-A267-875AE4A2B5AC_1_1743a34c-7409-4c7b-bc5f-33ad34bc3bd2.png",
            "title1": "Medication",
            "text1": "<p>There is no day in Bali where you don’t see a street dog in need. Most of them have skin conditions (scabies) and can be easily treated with the right medication. </p>"
          }
        },
        "4e59c6f7-156b-45da-9b8e-f36822f341c5": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Background_f2d0fbe6-e8b6-4b0a-adf1-19dc672bd6d1.png",
            "title1": "Dumped Puppies",
            "text1": "<p>Dumped puppies are very common. Left alone from young age, they either make it or not. Several rescuers take them in, treat them and try to find foster or forever homes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "288c812c-0f34-41bc-9029-ac3ac1819860": {
          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Background_1_2bd4236d-58e7-4e45-876a-4a6bf05b9fc2.png",
            "title1": "Traumas",
            "text1": "<p>Once a dog has been picked up from the streets you will also need to provide after care. It’s about socializing and building trust. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1637807530288d7dd5-0",
